title: Match history
body:
whenever i try to view my match history online it only comes with the site navigation bar at the top and a blank white box below it no matter what match im trying to view this happens.

does anyone know if there is a fix to this or any other way to view matches.

replies.body: Your browser may be having an issue yielding your results.  You may need to clear your [cache ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies)to fix this up.  You can also run Incognito or another browser to see if that helps.  If the issue persists let me know, as well as a screenshot if possible!

after clearing my cache and trying an incognito window the problem has not been fixed
http://imgur.com/a/Ux1gt
thank you for your time
I'm looking at your profile and everything looks okay.  What happens if you click on [this link](http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-history/NA/39843670)?
The same screen as seen in the above picture appears when I click the given link

Gonna link my post from the other thread as well
